  "texts": [
    "Task SetupWe used the graduate admission task as our testbed.",
    "To ensure manageable study durations and prevent participant fatigue, we selected five task cases based on the length of the pilot study.",
    "These cases included one for the tutorial and four for the main tasks.",
    "To investigate human-AI deliberation, we selected cases from a pilot study where human and AI opinions conflicted, often involving ambiguous applicant profiles near the admission borderline.",
    "As a result, predicting the admission outcome for these cases was challenging for both humans and AI, leading to performance levels between 50% and 60% for both."
